# Channels

## Create channel
### End point
/api/channel/create
### Method Type
POST
### Status code
201
### Request Input Schema
Key| Description| Constraints
|---------|-----------|----------
|name| name of new channel| Required, alphanumeric, max:20
|type| public or private| Required
|team_id| ID of the team in which channel is created| Required, numeric
|Description| Description of channel| max:100
### Headers
Key| Description| Constraints
|---------|-----------|----------
Token| Token for authentication| Required
### Response
Key| Description
|---------|-----------
|name |Channel name
|message| success message for channel creation
|type| private/public


